<p>I humbly suggest that next, you impose on a therapist.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.littleblur.com">Ben Donley</a>
 on February  7, 2007 <a href="imposition#c1" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
