<div id="c6">
<p>Some of the behavior you describe, especially the unwillingness to &#8220;bother&#8221; others, sounds like introversion.</p>

<p>There&#8217;s plenty to read about introversion online.  I suggest the article <a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/doc/200303/rauch" rel="nofollow">&#8220;Caring for Your Introvert&#8221;</a>.</p>

<p>Also, the book <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Introvert-Advantage-Thrive-Extrovert-World/dp/0761123695" rel="nofollow">The Introvert Advantage</a>, although a bit pop-psy, is very informative.</p>

<p>(introversion != shyness)</p>

