<p><i>This, I suppose, is the actual problem: I feel my existence is an imposition on the planet.</i></p>

<p>I felt like that for a long time. Then one day I looked at what I&#8217;d done in my life to that point and decided that it was enough, that I had contributed enough to the world to pay back what I&#8217;d cost it. And after that I didn&#8217;t worry about it so much.</p>

